Siguro ganoon din sana ang magiging desisyon ko.

274
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,120
"Siya"?

275
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,440
Sino ang "siya"?

276
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,680
Isang miyembro ng pamilya.

277
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,680
Pamilya?

278
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,040
Hindi ko alam kung paano kita papasayahin,

279
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,640
