299
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,200
Sige.

300
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,600
Sige, tama na. Mabuti.

301
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,400
Dito.

302
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:02,920
- Okay.
- Dito.

303
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,960
Mainit na sopas ng isda.

304
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:12,920
- Heto, tikman mo.
- Sige.

305
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
