418
00:27:07,361 --> 00:27:08,761
"Bakit ba lagi ka na lang sunud-sunuran?"

419
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,280
"Dapat may gulugod ang isang lalaki."

420
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:11,360
"Hindi mo ba alam 'yan?"

421
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,320
Paano ko hindi malalaman iyon?

422
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,480
Ramdam ko lang na

423
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,176
