436
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,880
Bueno, isa akong guro, kung tutuusin.

437
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,040
Sa totoo lang, ang nanay ni Xing Wu,

438
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,480
