447
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:03,600
Papalit-palit ang mga taas at baba.

448
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,600
Medyo katulad lang ito ng buhay natin.

449
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,696
Tingnan mo, baka ikaw ay

450
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,240
